features: 2025 Upgraded Bluetooth 5.4 and effortless pairing: The wireless earbuds use latest Bluetooth 5.4 technology, with 85% faster audio data transmission speed, uninterrupted and stable transmission, and lower energy consumption (up to 15 meters), allowing you to easily control music and calls at home, in the office or anywhere; After the initial connection, just take the bluetooth earphones out of the charging case, the device will automatically pair with the earbuds.

75-Hour Playback and LED Digital Display: Wireless headphones can listen for 15 hours on a single charge, earphones can be fully charged for more use time, and the attached portable charging box can extend the playback time to 75 hours. Bluetooth earbuds adopts intelligent LED digital display screen, so you can easily know the battery consumption of ear buds wireless bluetooth and charging box, so as to master the charging time. You don't have to worry about battery life even on a long trip.

High-Fidelity Stereo Sound and Clear Calls: Our bluetooth headphones with 14.2mm vibrating diaphragm and AAC/SBC audio coding technology that delivers powerful bass, smooth mids, and clear treble bringing you an immersive and powerful sound experience. The wireless earphones feature a high-quality ENC noise-canceling microphone that passively cancels 90% of background noise, you can enjoy a best-in-class call experience whether you’re at the gym, on the go, or in a noisy environment.

Ergonomic Sports Design and IP7 Waterproof: The noise cancelling headphones features ear hooks made of an innovative TPE (elastic) material, the ultra-light and ergonomic design allows you to wear them for a long time without feeling uncomfortable. Try the three tip sizes to get snug sport earbuds fit and create a perfect seal for crystal clear sound. Running headphones are waterproof with IP7 technology, so you can take rain, and light sweat without breaking.

Smart Touch Controls and Wide Compatibility: Earphones wireless bluetooth with high sensitivity touch technology, and it can help you easily achieve multiple functions, including play/pause, answer/reject phone, volume adjustment, switch music, activate voice assistant, etc. Over ear earbuds are compatible with most Bluetooth music players including cellphones, tablets, computers, TV, etc.
